nodes.text: The Battle of Ord Janon took place in the first year of the Clone Wars and resulted in a victory for the Galactic Republic. The victory lead the Republic media to report that the Separatists were on the run. Count Dooku, labeled Republic reports mentioning the Confederate withdrawal from the "temporary" worlds of Ord Janon and Raxus Prime as "spurious" in a response transmitted by the CIS Shadowfeed.
